{"tid":1445843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"停一停","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:35:02.000Z","uid":286008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"60d4b210f44618e82feb697946fb083b6d8215f5","tid":1445843,"uid":286008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"成場運動已經過左一段時間。雖然大家撚狗撚得好開心，但係班狗比人撚左咁多次都學精左。同埋咁耐以來五大訴求都係未能達到。<br />\n<br />\n所以來緊係咪要將勇武戰線果邊停一停休一休息先。另外有部分和理非開始對成場運動卻步，所以既然係咁不如就擴展番和理非條戰線。搵人再搞多次百萬大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n一來可以稍為比勇武義士們休息一下，重新制定策略。二來都可以重新吸納班遊離中間派。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9166366bf0991b22ba084c3924b12799d77d035a","tid":1445843,"uid":286008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:32:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2e30dff6204cdd64e820a7de001f2c1431324e9","tid":1445843,"uid":286008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"76087b4a432235f7cdbb82f110b07fe1b20425d5","tid":1445843,"uid":286008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"db184710ab8b7fee5eaf078f1bed8749da20dcc8","tid":1445843,"uid":286008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb795fdb407fa8c39ae511c6335b9a29045e91e4","tid":1445843,"uid